{"tid":1451572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過811","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:08:54.000Z","uid":217806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b537eef38f86fbceac2f4d6c2178a3431231218","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:06.000Z","msg":"要諗下依家個狀況而去做野<br />\n連儂牆 不了 要轉軚嘅其實都轉左<br />\n<br />\n玩地鐵 不了 阻住人返工對成件事成效不大 有人支持但只會令抗拒嘅人更加抗拒<br />\n<br />\n發夢 可以 但係好肯定咁講 只會一次比一次差 大家都知又有老解 又老屈 又恰女人 又扮示威者 又用過份武力 而大家嘅裝備好極有限 究竟係對示威者定狗嘅影響大d 大家其實心中有數 咁樣對成件事有冇好處呢 又或者咁講 政府會唔會驚呢 我諗光頭sir個句已經答到你<br />\n<br />\n所以其實係要做d令政府<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驚</span></span>嘅野<br />\n<br />\n機場 經濟 三罷 其實都走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n最唔想嘅狀況係通過勇武去進行抗爭 雖然我地已經用左  但唔代表我地唔可以用返所謂和理非嘅方法 <br />\n<br />\n經過左2個月 究竟勇武 仲可唔可以 達成我地嘅目標呢  我並唔係講勇武唔實際 只係經過811 勇武已經唔係最有效嘅手法<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\nBe water, my friend<span style=\"color: maroon;\">s</span>"},{"pid":"137d48c58d079ac2e0a6bff39a82c1df1c0a0cd8","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8688cb4bfada458708ab0cd56e12befbea1e0c3","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c3246c82d5c96c13e93eb136fab5896128afea","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eac1d5003ea03563bb906c922d28fe9981253c","tid":1451572,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:52:54.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d74fe03af8f7b7dc010b0e500812c623e4d10a4e","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffec9660acb9c3a29808caeb34eb7b969a2faa38","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ce790c59597ca52265ad704eb529e12d594522","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2696cef4cd722bda06f3b2ea3870ffd4335fd634","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd22a70ba835847ac535d9be05420c2a28bc7a7","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e457d9bcdb3b21f1e797d8109e6e85d3d1292d","tid":1451572,"uid":288348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:51.000Z","msg":"柒婆成日話經濟重要 就搞佢經濟 等班商家佬都驚<br />\n先影響到狗官<br />\n你同班狗勇武 柒婆理得你死"},{"pid":"5df9591e1062c7a7259b43c66367d3a8b29f6d2b","tid":1451572,"uid":217806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae37ff0575c61e15b83e8ccd